’Ł@18f8550a585ec3aeba82df247ba3ff2f1cfd4dfabe0371adf1da32bc13d87a72Ś4Title: title: help externs
Path: Examples
Content:
Show all externs.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> help externs


```
Show help for single extern.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> help externs smth


```
Search for string in extern names and descriptions.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> help externs --find smth


```
